,"count":1},{"word":"trigger","count":1},{"word":"immediate","count":1},{"word":"explosion","count":1},{"word":"test","count":1},{"word":"durability","count":1},{"word":"physically","count":1},{"word":"impacting","count":1},{"word":"functional","count":1},{"word":"specs","count":1},{"word":"send","count":1},{"word":"search","count":1},{"word":"warehouse","count":1},{"word":"substitutes","count":1},{"word":"standard","count":1},{"word":"easily","count":1},{"word":"contain","count":1},{"word":"substance","count":1},{"word":"help","count":1},{"word":"neutralize","count":1},{"word":"toxicity","count":1},{"word":"allow","count":1},{"word":"sea","count":1},{"word":"flames","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"fancy","count":1},{"word":"spoil","count":1},{"word":"fun","count":1},{"word":"afraid","count":1},{"word":"suspend","count":1},{"word":"race","count":1},{"word":"found","count":1},{"word":"near","count":1},{"word":"north","count":1},{"word":"resonance","count":1},{"word":"beacon","count":1},{"word":"functioning","count":1},{"word":"properly","count":1},{"word":"issue","count":1},{"word":"investigate","count":1},{"word":"often","count":1},{"word":"detect","count":1},{"word":"danger","count":1},{"word":"discords","count":1},{"word":"regard","count":1},{"word":"sensitive","count":1},{"word":"change","count":1},{"word":"frequencies","count":1},{"word":"surroundings","count":1},{"word":"gulpuffs","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"haywire","count":1},{"word":"suppose","count":1},{"word":"check","count":1},{"word":"perhaps","count":1},{"word":"games'","count":1},{"word":"resonated","count":1},{"word":"lack","count":1},{"word":"perceivable","count":1},{"word":"typically","count":1},{"word":"suggests","count":1},{"word":"unknown","count":1},{"word":"risks","count":1},{"word":"safe","count":1},{"word":"job","count":1},{"word":"successfully","count":1},{"word":"prevented","count":1},{"word":"potential","count":1},{"word":"td","count":1},{"word":"outbreak","count":1},{"word":"requested","count":1},{"word":"compared","count":1},{"word":"previous","count":1},{"word":"outbreaks","count":1},{"word":"done","count":1},{"word":"thank","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"identical","count":1},{"word":"expert","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"definitive","count":1},{"word":"conclusions","count":1},{"word":"sample","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"colleague","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"hands","count":1},{"word":"specializes","count":1},{"word":"ecoacoustic","count":1},{"word":"expertise","count":1},{"word":"trust","count":1},{"word":"rest","count":1},{"word":"assured","count":1},{"word":"careful","count":1},{"word":"samples","count":1},{"word":"especially","count":1},{"word":"valuable","count":1},{"word":"wake-up","count":1},{"word":"call","count":1},{"word":"answers","count":1},{"word":"searching","count":1},{"word":"games","count":1},{"word":"people","count":1},{"word":"looking","count":1},{"word":"probably","count":1},{"word":"wanted","count":1},{"word":"discuss","count":1},{"word":"holding","count":1},{"word":"event","count":1},{"word":"date","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"else","count":1},{"word":"going","count":1},{"word":"lab","count":1},{"word":"fully","count":1},{"word":"charged","count":1},{"word":"energy","count":1},{"word":"missed","count":1},{"word":"greetings","count":1},{"word":"general","count":1},{"word":"rover","count":1},{"word":"established","count":1},{"word":"connection","count":1},{"word":"electric","count":1},{"word":"capacitor","count":1},{"word":"damaged","count":1},{"word":"simply","count":1},{"word":"put","count":1},{"word":"fortunately","count":1},{"word":"backup","count":1},{"word":"repair","count":1},{"word":"charge","count":1},{"word":"questions","count":1},{"word":"theory","count":1},{"word":"practice","count":1},{"word":"difficult","count":1},{"word":"dodge","count":1},{"word":"attack","count":1},{"word":"perfect","count":1},{"word":"hit","count":1},{"word":"kill","count":1},{"word":"gravely","count":1},{"word":"injured","count":1},{"word":"dead","count":1},{"word":"threnodians","count":1},{"word":"proven","count":1},{"word":"stronger","count":1},{"word":"imagined","count":1},{"word":"handle","count":1},{"word":"ovathrax","count":1},{"word":"certainly","count":1},{"word":"barrier","count":1},{"word":"ancient","count":1},{"word":"dates","count":1},{"word":"founding","count":1},{"word":"creating","count":1},{"word":"limited","count":1},{"word":"technology","count":1},{"word":"whoever","count":1},{"word":"truly","count":1},{"word":"genius","count":1},{"word":"unleash","count":1},{"word":"launch","count":1},{"word":"entire","count":1},{"word":"place","count":1},{"word":"air","count":1},{"word":"matter","count":1},{"word":"fast","count":1},{"word":"build","count":1},{"word":"long","count":1},{"word":"mass","count":1},{"word":"destruction","count":1},{"word":"capital","count":1},{"word":"strict","count":1},{"word":"control","count":1},{"word":"assume","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"approve","count":1},{"word":"application","count":1},{"word":"alright","count":1},{"word":"waiting","count":1},{"word":"green","count":1},{"word":"light","count":1},{"word":"lastly","count":1},{"word":"please","count":1},{"word":"fill","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Sorry for the delay. Even for someone like me, digging up old records takes time. Your request is from years ago, after all.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Here's the short version: we still have some spare parts from the Explosive Spears used in the last battle, stored in the Port City of Guixu. They should work if we assemble them.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"With such a weapon, you should be able to breach the Inferno Rider's shield and deliver a powerful blow to the Tacet Mark core of the Incinero Petals.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"I just came across some records while researching Tacetite weapons. The spears were developed in collaboration between Huaxu Academy and the <ano=CSC>Court of Savantae</ano> back then.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"They were obsessed with making weapons with overwhelming firepower, completely disregarding practicality and safety. Typical of those savants.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"The CSC were known for their wild ideas, but the \"Orange Box\" group was the most outrageous of all.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"According to the records, the spare spears were split into three parts and stored in three different research centers, for security reasons.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"After all these years, I'm unsure if they still work. But if you can find them, I can guide you on how to assemble and recalibrate them.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Wait a moment. Something seems wrong with these <color=Highlight>barrels</color>.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"I checked the records again, and it turns out a lot of these spare barrels are defective. They were actually meant to be destroyed.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"If you were to make an Explosive Spear with defective parts, it could trigger an immediate explosion.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"That’s why you should test the durability of those barrels on the spot by by physically impacting them. You'll need at least three functional <color=Highlight>barrels</color>.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Just find the specs and send them over. Then we can search the warehouse for similar barrels to use as substitutes.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"You're right, {PlayerName}. If they were standard <color=Highlight>barrels</color>, they wouldn't break so easily.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"And those <color=Highlight>defective barrels</color>, once destroyed, contain a substance that can help neutralize the toxicity of Incinero Petals. This should allow you to stay in the Sea of Flames a bit longer.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"{PlayerName}, fancy seeing you here.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"I don't want to spoil your fun, but I'm afraid we need to suspend the race for now.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"I checked the monitoring data as you asked, and I found unusual fluctuations near the upper waters to the north.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"The Resonance Beacon is functioning properly, but we still don't know why it didn't issue a warning this time. I will investigate this further at a later time.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Animals are often the first to detect signs of danger.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Tacet Discords are similar to animals in this regard. They're very sensitive to any change in the frequencies in their surroundings. That's why those Gulpuffs went haywire.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"I suppose that's why you asked me to check the monitoring data for you, Jiyan?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"Perhaps the Riverside Games' frequency resonated with something in the upper waters?","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"The lack of perceivable warning signs typically suggests unknown risks. Jiyan, {PlayerName}, stay safe.","quest_name":"Riverside Games","quest_id":125000080},{"text":"...We're no longer seeing any unusual fluctuations now.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"Good job. You should have successfully prevented a potential TD Outbreak.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"As you requested, I compared the fluctuations with those of the previous Outbreaks, and I did spot some similarities.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"I'm not done yet. Thank me later if you must.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"Though there are some similarities, they aren't identical. I'm no expert in this field, and I can't give you any definitive conclusions yet.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"Frequency sample from a Sonoro Sphere... I'll deliver it to a colleague. It's in better hands with her.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"It's someone you know. Baizhi. She specializes in Ecoacoustic research, and the Sonoro Sphere is her field of expertise.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"What now, you don't trust me?","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"Rest assured. You should know how careful we are with our samples... Especially such a valuable one.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"It's a wake-up call, and it may also hold the answers we've been searching for all these years.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"By the way, the Riverside Games people were looking for you, Jiyan. Probably wanted to discuss holding the event again at a later date.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"Now, if there's nothing else, I'm going back to my lab.","quest_name":"Pastures Like Old Times","quest_id":125000082},{"text":"The Disruptor is fully charged and ready to fire. But...","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"It takes a lot of energy to fire the Disruptor. If we missed...","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Greetings, General Jiyan, Rover.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"We've got good news and bad news. Good news is, we've established connection to the Disruptor and we're ready to go.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Bad news is, the Disruptor’s electric capacitor is damaged.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Simply put, it’s out of power.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Fortunately, there should be a backup power outlet.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"To use the Disruptor, we'll have to repair that outlet first, then wait for a full charge.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Any questions?","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"In theory, we could. In practice, it's difficult.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"First, it could dodge our attack. Not even a perfect hit can kill it. It will be gravely injured, but not dead.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Threnodians have been proven to be way stronger than we imagined. Our Disruptor can't handle the Ovathrax, but it can certainly break through that Barrier.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"That's because this ancient Disruptor dates back at least to the founding of Jinzhou.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Creating such a powerful weapon with limited technology back then… whoever did it was truly a genius, I must say.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"If we were to unleash its full power on Jinzhou city, it might launch the entire place into the air.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"...I can, but it takes time.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"No matter how fast I build it... Jinzhou won't be able to hold out that long.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"By the way, this is a weapon of mass destruction... The Capital would want strict control over its use, I assume?","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Will they really approve our application?","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Alright, we’ll be waiting for the green light.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004},{"text":"Lastly, we've got more bad news... Baizhi, please fill us in.","quest_name":"Grand Warstorm","quest_id":140000004}]}